{"tid":1783262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"爆料！你食緊嘅真喺美國進口豬肉咩？","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T14:16:10.000Z","uid":47113,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"042828e91bdb9170bb6a37bee91ab60646289625","tid":1783262,"uid":47113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPgui6z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPgui6z.png&h=d4138de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近我菲律賓工人話，有得買<span style=\"color: gold;\">美國</span>進口豬肉，仲叫食神蹈哥嚟賣廣告。講緊嘅喺而家誠哥個間X佳賣個種，話就話係<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國Smithfield</span>生產，但其實前幾年喺一單好著名嘅收購案，已經比<span style=\"color: red;\">萬洲國際</span>收購咗。<br />\n<br />\n咁大家又知唔知萬洲（香港上市），又有咩生意會做？萬州最出名就喺大陸嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">雙匯腸仔</span>。咁中國名牌雙匯腸仔最出喺咩？自己Google 下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再中伏啦！唔好以為自己喺食緊美帝嘢就一定喺比佢地賺錢啦。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8F%B2%E5%AF%86%E6%96%AF%E8%8F%B2%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%258F%25B2%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%2581&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=56caaa25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8F%B2%E5%AF%86%E6%96%AF%E8%8F%B2%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81</a>"},{"pid":"af9371f64757441942a90d491b36cc0e08caaaf7","tid":1783262,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:57:06.000Z","